column16: Nelson Cruz homers (5) on a fly ball to left center field.   Lance Berkman scores.    Adrian Beltre scores.
Adrian Beltre walks.  Wild pitch by pitcher David Carpenter.   Ian Kinsler scores.    Lance Berkman to 2nd.
Lance Berkman singles on a ground ball to center fielder Peter Bourjos.   Craig Gentry scores.    David Murphy scores.    Ian Kinsler to 3rd.
Ian Kinsler walks.   A.  J.   Pierzynski scores.    Craig Gentry to 3rd.    David Murphy to 2nd.
